* {{ill|Minato Shrine (Izumo-taisha)|ja|湊社|12=draft}} ({{ill|Izumo|ja|出雲市|12=draft}}, Shimane Prefecture)
* Kashima Shrine (Zōfu Shrine) (Izumo, Shimane Prefecture)
* {{ill|Homori Shrine|ja|火守神社|12=draft}} (Izumo, Shimane Prefecture)
* Kushiyatama Shrine ({{ill|Minabe|ja|みなべ町|12=draft}}, Wakayama Prefecture)

